des: Real People KS Radio is a Christian based radio station where we believe in the Holy Bible, and the power of the Holy Spirit. We believe that Jesus Christ came, and died for our sins so that we can be saved. Our Radio Ministry is here to provide kingdom solutions from the Word of God to the broken and the lost. We promote love, encouragement and healing to all people around the world. We play contemporary Christian, Reggae Gospel and Culturally clean music. Our spoken language is predominantly English, and we love all people.
